<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-6787] assassinate should continue when the endpoint vanishes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6787</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Assassinate can NPE in various situations, most notably if the endpoint vanishes during the sleep-for-safety check.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
